Merge pull request #522 from Leonidas-from-XIV/parse-string-promise

Parse string promise

Minimal version is Node 8

Create a promise-specific version of parseString

Examples:

```js
// Via root API
xml2js.parseStringPromise('< ... >', options)
  .then(function (result) { /* ... */ })
  .catch(function (err) { /* ... */ })

// Via parser
var parser = new xml2js.Parser(options);
parser.parseStringPromise('< ... >')
  .then(function (result) { /* ... */ })
  .catch(function (err) { /* ... */ })
```
